### `trade_bill_chain_records` (Trade bill context)
On-chain confirmation record. One per confirmed draft.

| Column | Type | Notes |
|--------|------|-------|
| `id` | text PK | |
| `draft_id` | text NN → `trade_bill_drafts.id` | |
| `network` | text NN | `testnet`, `mainnet`, `futurenet` |
| `contract_id` | text NN | Deployed `TradeBillRegistry` contract ID |
| `chain_bill_id` | text NN | `u64` from the contract event |
| `tx_hash` | text NN | Stellar transaction hash |
| `ledger` / `issued_at_ledger` | text | Ledger data |
| `created_at_ms` | text NN | |

Unique index: `(chain_bill_id, contract_id, network)` — prevents duplicate confirmations.

